        <dcterms:accessRights>This ontology is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License (CC BY-NC 4.0). It allows non-commercial use, sharing, and adaptation of the ontology, as long as users provide clear credit to the creator by citing the ontology&apos;s title, creator, and license information. Commercial use is strictly prohibited.</dcterms:accessRights>
